15 Q. Do you recall telling, either by text
16 message or in-person, Mr. Isaacman to burn the boats;
17 we're going to war.
18 A. Yes.
19 Q. And what did you mean by that?
20 A. I don't know, something stupid.
21 Q. What were you referring to with that
22 statement?
23 A. I have no idea. I say a lot of stupid
